      AVG(TOTAL.CUSTOMEDFIN) CUSTOMEDFIN, AVG(TOTAL.CUSTOMEDREAL) CUSTOMEDREAL, SUM(TOTAL.VLTABELA) VLTABELA, SUM(TOTAL.PESOBRUTO) PESOBRUTO,
